currently charges $1500-2000 per week per client, preferring
weekly sprints over hourly billing.
(https://grain.com/share/recording/a89d172c-2056-41ca-9bd5-dc004efd3641/7QL=
tJb8djbgTQlHJgrXU36xzKOHUkNRmtuib2ShE?t=3D534636)Sean
struggles to acquire better clients and scale his business
without being overly hands-on.Experiences burnout from managing
multiple hands-on projects and clients.
