tJb8djbgTQlHJgrXU36xzKOHUkNRmtuib2ShE?t=3D239538)Desires
to transition to a consulting role rather than managing
day-to-day tasks.
(https://grain.com/share/recording/a89d172c-2056-41ca-9bd5-dc004efd3641/7QL=
tJb8djbgTQlHJgrXU36xzKOHUkNRmtuib2ShE?t=3D429916)Consulting
